flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[Read seed or use process ID]
    B --> C[Print heading]
    C --> D[Set iteration to 1]
    D --> E{Iteration <= 200?}
    E -- No --> K[Print final newline]
    K --> L[Exit]
    E -- Yes --> F[Print current value]
    F --> G{Current value even?}
    G -- Yes --> H[Divide value by 2]
    G -- No --> I[Set value to value * 3 + 1]
    H --> J[Print line break every 10 values]
    I --> J
    J --> M[Increment iteration]
    M --> E
